---
title: Caramelised Beef Rump & Onion Subs with Fries, Avocado & Herby Mayo
description: When you’re short on time but craving something you can devour with all your favourite components, a beef sub is the only
option. Make it your own by customising it with caramelised onions, avocado and a creamy herb mayo. Add a side of fries and
you’ll be humming in bliss!

